_:N47cceb4887aa445097bc95f1c1bd678a <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Peter became the Permanent Secretary at the Department for Work and Pensions on 16 January 2018.</p>\n\n<p>Previously he has worked:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>as Director General for Finance at <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> from July 2016</li>\n  <li>as Director General for Housing and Planning at the Department for Communities and Local Government</li>\n  <li>as Director of the Enterprise and Growth Unit at HM Treasury</li>\n  <li>as a director in the Shareholder Executive</li>\n  <li>on secondment to 3i PLC</li>\n  <li>in a number of roles, including Private Secretary to the Chief Secretary, at HM Treasury</li>\n</ul>\n\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
